headline: McKay Brothers and Quincy Data Expand Best-in-Class Cross-Border Market Interconnection Between Ontario and the US
summary: McKay Brothers, a global provider of fast connectivity between financial market venues, and its sister company Quincy Data, a distributor of time-sensitive market data, have expanded services linking key Canadian financial markets with major US trading hubs in Illinois and New Jersey.
